Coming Out to my Mom wasnt such a great Idea. Doing so has caused her to Hate all my Friends especially my Best Friend Jen. She Threatend that she would take out all my that she wants me to be normal. She called Jen and Left a harrasing message hich went like this " You Fucking Whore I am Declaring War on You. You better have a good attorney because im sending you to jail". What Gets me is Jen hasnt done anything illegal. My mom has seen the pics from yaoi con w/ like me making out w/ boys but what shes gonna blame that on Jen. I was a big Fucking Fairy Before I met Jen. Anywayz I confronted my mom about the message she denied it at first and then admitted to it she then started hitting me so I pushed her off b/c I wanted her to stop. She hit the wall behind her I didnt want to hurt her I just wanted her to stop. Then My Stepfather pushed me onto the bed and started to strangle me. My mom just watched and yelled at what a disgusting freak I was as I laid on the bed Suffocating my stepdad didnt care if he killed me I could tell by seeing the hatred in his eyes. If my sister had not come in screaming then god knows what have happend. They told me to pack my things and leave and If I want to come back I have to beg for mercy, become straight and lie to myself, have no friends, and have no freewill. They took away my cell and car. Im going to stay w/ Jen for a while till Ive gotten a new Job. Ive already found a car I just need the job to get it and I should be able to get my own apartment in a month (I Hope). I only regret having to leave my sister alone in that mad house. 

Well post later

Lets see now starting from thursday. Got my Things ready for Otakucon and drove down to Boca to Jen's House. We spent the day going store to store looking for "Tokyo a go go Bratz Dolls" which was fun. I even bought one for myself why you ask b/c he sorta looks like me. then stayed up playing with the 5 bratz dolls the cafe, and the sushi lounge how fun. Even though all we made them do was beat each other up and have sex um...yeah were cool.Then went to Denny's for breakfast/dinner. Friday-Attempted to go to Miami cause the con started at 6pm. The turnpike was full of traffic/assholes b/c of one car accident we let one person get in front of us then 30 people cut us of and nearly hit us so were like fuck this and the con. We get off at Commercial and find ourselves at the porn store. People stared us like we were weird oh yeah thats right im dressed as a murderer (Akabane) and Jen's Dressed up as Orochimaru (carrying around a plushy snake that apperas to be real). We meet this weird guy who was little odd. Then we wnt for sushi yum and had Banana Tempura and some mochii. Went back to Jen's house watched Dragon Drive then went to sleep. Woke up Saturday morning got ready me cosplaying as Goku and Jen as Sanzo. Picked up Ken and then off to miami we went. Unfortunatly we had to park like 9 blocks away and walk to the con. We took some picks Sanzo spent way to much money on Yaoi, got our picks taken, bought a real coyote tail ^_^, Got to see Johnny young Bosch  who is a really cool voice actor and ex-power ranger. Got to see his band play and then we went home. Stopped at Dennys to eat I didnt wake up till 2 and figured it was a little late to go to the con so we stayed back watched Gad Guard and came home . THE END. 

post later and maybe somke picks from the con
